5
00:00:09,980 --> 00:00:12,500
[Previously]
Have you never tried it before?

6
00:00:12,780 --> 00:00:13,860
No.

7
00:00:14,660 --> 00:00:18,020
Geez, why would you think of him?

8
00:00:18,020 --> 00:00:20,660
Don’t even think about it, Kaew.

9
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:24,580
Will you please allow me to get to know you more?

10
00:00:25,060 --> 00:00:30,740
Don’t let your feelings grow too far, or else you might regret it later.

11
00:00:30,740 --> 00:00:31,860
Khun Yai !

12
00:00:31,860 --> 00:00:32,820
Khun Yai.

13
00:00:32,820 --> 00:00:34,820
- Khun Yai.
- Shhh!

14
00:00:34,820 --> 00:00:36,820
Did you send him to spy on them?

15
00:00:36,820 --> 00:00:39,700
I must apologise for causing you trouble, Uncle.

16
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:42,380
I’m willing to do anything for our country.

17
00:00:42,380 --> 00:00:44,580
Sir, Khun Prom is here.

18
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:46,300
- Kan!
- Yes, sir.

19
00:00:46,300 --> 00:00:49,980
Go stall time for me. Tell him I’ll be there when I’m done with my business.

20
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:56,800
Ruedee.

21
00:00:59,460 --> 00:01:00,460
Wait!

22
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:11,000
Is someone injured?

23
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:15,600
Yes, sir. It’s just a fight between servants.

24
00:01:20,060 --> 00:01:21,860
Is it that serious?

25
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:34,800
Prom.

26
00:01:46,930 --> 00:01:49,600
What matter has brought you here?

27
00:01:50,900 --> 00:01:53,100
I see Khun Phra Nai coming to visit this place almost every day,

28
00:01:53,820 --> 00:01:56,700
so I’m curious what it is that he finds interesting here.

29
00:01:57,930 --> 00:02:00,540
I’m merely here to talk about musical instruments with Uncle.

30
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:04,330
You already know that he is my treble fiddle’s teacher.

31
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:09,380
I was only joking.

32
00:02:10,020 --> 00:02:14,980
As a matter of fact, Father has asked me to deliver this to you.

33
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:18,180
These are fruits from our orchard.

34
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,500
How considerate.

35
00:02:22,740 --> 00:02:25,820
Actually, you don’t need to come bearing any gift.

36
00:02:25,820 --> 00:02:30,340
Just a greeting would already make an old man like me happy.

37
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:32,260
Please don’t say that.

38
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:37,620
Father said his adopted son often comes here to bother you.

39
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,380
So, he’d like to return the gratitude somehow.

40
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,460
I must be going then.

41
00:02:57,060 --> 00:03:01,500
Do you think your brother honestly wanted to pay me a visit?

42
00:03:02,730 --> 00:03:03,940
Of course not.

43
00:03:04,380 --> 00:03:07,940
Even if it’s Father’s order, a man like Prom…

44
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,660
would never do it if he doesn’t want to.

45
00:03:12,730 --> 00:03:15,800
Then, why do you think he came here?

46
00:03:18,130 --> 00:03:20,780
I’d like to know that too.

47
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:47,100
